
Assignment 2 Little Brother

Run the project with commands like these:
./pistatsd.py -b localhost -k first -p rabbit_vhost -c rabbit_user:rabbit_pass
./pistatsview.py -b localhost -k first -p rabbit_vhost -c rabbit_user:rabbit_pass

./pistatsd.py -b localhost -k first
./pistatsview.py -b localhost -k first

RabbitMQ installation and setup
	sudo apt-get update
	sudo apt-get install rabbitmq-server

	use the following for enabling remote connection
		sudo rabbitmqctl add_user "rabbit_user" "rabbit_pass"
		sudo rabbitmqctl add_vhost "rabbit_vhost"
		sudo rabbitmqctl set_permissions -p "rabbit_vhost" "rabbit_user"  ".*" ".*" ".*"

	run rabbit scripts with destination ip like:
		python rabbit_pub 127.0.0.1
		

Required External Libraries:
    pika
    psutil (only required for pistatsd)
    pymongo (only required for pistatsview)
